Pre-Game Insights: The Opta supercomputer predicts that Equatorial Guinea has a 39.4% chance of winning the match, while Guinea-Bissau has a 33.8% chance.
This will be the first encounter between Equatorial Guinea and Guinea-Bissau at the CAF Africa Cup of Nations.
Equatorial Guinea and Guinea-Bissau last met in March 2022, with Guinea-Bissau winning 3-0.
Equatorial Guinea could go unbeaten in their opening two games of an Africa Cup of Nations for the third time out of four participations.
